Who am I?

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:34.170 align:middle line:90%
Don't know.

00:13:34.170 --> 00:13:36.760 align:middle line:90%
That's all you need to do.

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:40.350 align:middle line:84%
Then he said, you
